headline: Hims & Hers Health surges on acquisition for at-home testing
summary: Hims & Hers Health (HIMS) stock gains on news that the company acquired Trybe Labs, which will allow the telehealth company to offer at-home testing. The deal will create competition for Labcorp (LH) and Quest (DGX) Julie Hyman and Seana Smith outline what investors need to know. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination here. This post was written by Naomi Buchanan.
